PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROY H. PIOVESANA, of Thunder Bay, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Patricia E. Wright, whose term has expired.
